products.title: Blueberry Imported 125g
products.body_html: Blueberries are also called bilberries in some parts of Europe. It is highly nutritious, loaded with numerous health benefits, and comes with a great taste, making it a favourite of many. It is believed to be the king of antioxidant foods. These are often labelled as a superfood because they are filled with health benefits. Our vendor sources blueberries from Australia, Canada, Chile, India, and the USA: Blueberries are perennial flowering plants with blue or purple berries. They are covered in a protective coating of powdery epicuticle wax, colloquially known as the "bloom", and have a sweet taste when mature, with variable acidity.

products.title: Dira Frozen Blackberry 500G
products.body_html:
Dira Frozen Blackberry IQF 500G

IQF means Individually Quick Frozen:
Each fruit piece is frozen individually for 10 max 15 minutes, making it easy to portion and preventing fruit from sticking together.

IQF freezing is the best way to preserve the natural taste & colour of fresh fruit. Using this technique, vitamins and nutrients are maintained, making frozen fruits just as healthy as fresh fruits.
